WEBVTT

00:10.867 --> 00:12.065
<i> PREVIOUSLY ON "GREENLEAF"...</i>

00:12.067 --> 00:14.532
-WHAT IS THE PROBLEM?
-I'M GETTING RIPPED OFF.

00:14.534 --> 00:15.731
AH!

00:15.733 --> 00:17.965
-WHAT IS SHE ON? DID THEY SAY?
-OXYCODONE.

00:17.967 --> 00:20.065
THAT PRETTY LITTLE BUNNY
PRANCING AROUND YOUR PARTY,

00:20.067 --> 00:21.832
SHE'S INTO CRYPTOCURRENCY.

00:21.834 --> 00:24.265
BISHOP GREENLEAF,
YOU COME TO CHIDE ME

00:24.267 --> 00:25.565
FOR NOT COMING
TO SERVICE TODAY?

00:25.567 --> 00:28.898
TELL THE CHURCH LIKE ADULTS
THAT WE'RE GETTING DIVORCED.

00:28.900 --> 00:31.265
I JUST KEEP GETTING
THIS PAIN IN MY SIDE.

00:31.267 --> 00:32.332
MAYBE YOU'RE PREGNANT.

00:32.334 --> 00:33.899
[ GASPING ]

00:33.901 --> 00:35.165
THERE WASN'T ENOUGH
HEALTHY TISSUE LEFT

00:35.167 --> 00:36.998
TO PRESERVE
THE OVARIES.

00:37.000 --> 00:39.198
-I CAN'T HAVE CHILDREN?
-WHAT'S THIS?

00:39.200 --> 00:41.698
IT'S A DRAFT OF WHAT I THINK WE
SHOULD TELL THE CHURCH SUNDAY.

00:41.700 --> 00:43.765
FEEL FREE TO MAKE
ANY CHANGES YOU SEE FIT.

00:43.767 --> 00:45.865
THE DEACONS MAY
ASK YOU TO STEP UP.

00:45.867 --> 00:48.332
-STEP UP?
-TAKE OVER AS HEAD PASTOR.

00:48.334 --> 00:52.732
♪♪

00:52.734 --> 00:54.798
MM.

00:54.800 --> 00:57.065
[ INDISTINCT TALKING ON RADIO ]

00:57.067 --> 01:03.998
♪♪

01:04.000 --> 01:06.732
MAY I CLAIM
A MOMENT OF TIME?

01:06.734 --> 01:08.632
HOW MAY I BE OF SERVICE
TO YOU?

01:12.334 --> 01:15.865
MY REVISED PROPOSAL
OF WHAT WE'RE GOING TO SAY

01:15.867 --> 01:18.865
TO THE CONGREGATION ON SUNDAY
ABOUT OUR DIVORCE.

01:18.867 --> 01:23.265
AH, THE LONG-AWAITED
REWRITE.

01:23.267 --> 01:25.998
I ASSUME IT TAKES INTO ACCOUNT
HOW THE CHILDREN RESPONDED

01:26.000 --> 01:27.598
WHEN WE SAT THEM DOWN
AND TOLD THEM?

01:27.600 --> 01:31.198
YES,
I SOFTENED IT CONSIDERABLY.

01:31.200 --> 01:33.932
I'M STILL AMAZED
I DIDN'T SEE IT COMING

01:33.934 --> 01:35.532
AFTER ALL THE HIGH DRAMA.

01:35.534 --> 01:37.798
YEAH, I AS WELL.

01:37.800 --> 01:39.998
IT'S A TESTIMONY, I GUESS,

01:40.000 --> 01:44.365
TO HOW BADLY THEY WISHED
IT WAS OTHERWISE.

01:47.134 --> 01:48.699
WHAT, JAMES?

01:48.701 --> 01:50.299
YOU ALWAYS MANAGED
TO COAX FLOWERS

01:50.301 --> 01:53.765
OUT OF THE HARD GROUND
OF FACT.

01:53.767 --> 01:56.998
IT'S FINE.
MAY I HOLD ONTO A COPY OF THIS?

01:57.000 --> 01:58.665
THERE'S ONE BY YOUR BED.

01:58.667 --> 02:00.465
I'VE PRINTED IT
IN LARGE FONT

02:00.467 --> 02:04.198
SO THAT YOU CAN
READ IT ON SUNDAY.

02:04.200 --> 02:05.865
PERFECT. THANK YOU.

02:05.867 --> 02:08.732
AND YOU SHOULD ALSO KNOW
THAT I'VE ASKED CHARITY TO SING

02:08.734 --> 02:10.732
BECAUSE I WANT
THE PEOPLE TO KNOW

02:10.734 --> 02:15.799
THAT IT IS STILL GOING TO BE
THE GREENLEAF SHOW EVERY SUNDAY.

02:15.801 --> 02:18.465
I'M JUST CURIOUS HOW YOU PLAN
ON SAYING GOODBYE, I MEAN,

02:18.467 --> 02:20.998
BECAUSE THERE'S NOTHING IN THIS
WRITING THAT INDICATES --

02:21.000 --> 02:23.665
OH, HOW I WILL BE
FLOATING AWAY

02:23.667 --> 02:26.732
LIKE AN INUIT WOMAN
ON AN ICE FLOE?

02:26.734 --> 02:28.398
THAT YOU'LL BE
FOLLOWING THE LORD

02:28.400 --> 02:30.032
TO THE LAMB
TO WHICH HE LEADS YOU.

02:30.034 --> 02:33.065
WELL, MY LORD AND MYSELF
WILL BE STAYING PUT.

02:33.067 --> 02:35.199
WE ARE DIVORCING.
OH, I KNOW THAT.

02:35.201 --> 02:37.265
UH, MY ATTORNEY
IS CASHING MY CHECKS.

02:37.267 --> 02:39.132
I'M WELL AWARE
OF THE SITUATION,

02:39.134 --> 02:41.498
AND I HAVE PRAYED ABOUT
THIS CONSIDERABLY, JAMES,

02:41.500 --> 02:43.132
AND I HAVE COME
TO THE CONCLUSION

02:43.134 --> 02:46.765
THAT THE BEST THING FOR CALVARY
IS THAT I STAY ON.

02:46.767 --> 02:48.099
AFTER WE'RE DIVORCED?

02:48.101 --> 02:50.365
WE BUILT THIS CHURCH
TOGETHER,

02:50.367 --> 02:52.832
AND WE HAVE TENDED
OUR RESPECTIVE FLOCKS

02:52.834 --> 02:55.665
ON NEIGHBORING
HILLSIDES TOGETHER,

02:55.667 --> 02:59.632
AND I SEE NO REASONS
BESIDES THIS RIDICULOUS CUSTOM

02:59.634 --> 03:02.265
THAT I SHOULD BE
FORCED TO LEAVE NOW,

03:02.267 --> 03:04.531
ESPECIALLY CONSIDERING
THE CIRCUMSTANCES

03:04.533 --> 03:08.765
BY WHICH I HAVE HAD TO KEEP
MY DISTANCE FROM YOU PERSONALLY!

03:08.767 --> 03:12.865
♪♪

03:12.867 --> 03:14.732
WELL.

03:14.734 --> 03:16.365
WELL?

03:18.067 --> 03:20.998
WELL, AT THE EXPENSE
OF JOINING PILATE AND PHARAOH

03:21.000 --> 03:24.398
IN GOD'S HALL OF HIGHLY
MISTAKEN INDIVIDUALS,

03:24.400 --> 03:27.932
LET ME JUST SAY
I WILL BE PRAYING FOR YOU!

03:30.600 --> 03:32.265
♪ AMEN ♪

03:34.734 --> 03:35.998
♪ ALL RIGHT ♪

03:36.000 --> 03:37.465
♪ AMEN ♪

03:37.467 --> 03:40.398
♪ UH-HUH, HMM ♪

03:40.400 --> 03:42.832
♪ OOH-OOH, OOH ♪

03:45.934 --> 03:47.299
♪ WELL ♪

03:50.734 --> 03:53.865
♪ OH-OHH, OHH ♪

03:53.867 --> 03:59.198
♪ OOH, OOH, OOH, OOH ♪

03:59.200 --> 04:02.232
♪ AMEN, AMEN ♪
♪ OH ♪

04:05.667 --> 04:07.465
♪ YEAH ♪

