04:17.200 --> 04:21.265
♪♪

04:21.267 --> 04:24.065
[ BABY CRYING ]

04:24.067 --> 04:28.065
♪♪

04:28.067 --> 04:29.865
CHARITY.

04:29.867 --> 04:31.265
CHARITY.

04:31.267 --> 04:32.998
OH. WHAT?

04:33.000 --> 04:38.198
WAKE UP. DIDN'T YOU HEAR
THIS CHILD CRYING FOR YOU?

04:38.200 --> 04:40.399
WHEN?

04:42.467 --> 04:45.132
MARICEL SAID THAT
HE WAS CALLING FOR YOU

04:45.134 --> 04:47.199
SO LOUDLY
THAT SHE COULD HEAR IT

04:47.201 --> 04:49.998
ALL THE WAY DOWN THE HALL
AND INTO THE LAUNDRY ROOM.

04:50.000 --> 04:51.565
-WITH THE DRYER ON.
-WITH THE DRYER ON.

04:51.567 --> 04:52.632
PLEASE JUST GIVE --
JUST GIVE HIM TO ME.

04:52.634 --> 04:54.432
NO. NO.

04:54.434 --> 04:56.898
YOU ARE NOT GOING
ANYWHERE NEAR THAT CHILD

04:56.900 --> 04:59.032
UNTIL YOU'RE IN
YOUR RIGHT MIND.

04:59.034 --> 05:01.932
CHARITY...

05:01.934 --> 05:04.532
ARE YOU
UNDER THE INFLUENCE?

05:04.534 --> 05:06.132
I COULDN'T SLEEP, MAMA.

05:06.134 --> 05:08.465
I TOOK ONE PILL.
WHAT PILL?

05:08.467 --> 05:10.899
JUST OVER-THE-COUNTER PILLS,
MAMA!

05:10.901 --> 05:12.898
SHH! OKAY.
WHAT?

05:12.900 --> 05:15.498
I'M SORRY, BABY.

05:15.500 --> 05:17.965
JUST TAKE THE BABY OUT.
TAKE THE BABY OUT.

05:17.967 --> 05:20.532
[ CRYING CONTINUES ]

05:20.534 --> 05:22.798
I AM GOING TO TAKE
THIS WHOLE PHARMACY OF YOURS

05:22.800 --> 05:24.932
AND JUST THROW IT INTO THE
TOILET AND FLUSH IT RIGHT NOW.

05:24.934 --> 05:26.832
DON'T. DON'T YOU DARE.
DON'T.

05:26.834 --> 05:28.299
ALL RIGHT.
DON'T.

05:28.301 --> 05:33.999
ALL RIGHT.
I JUST -- I NEEDED SLEEP.

05:34.001 --> 05:35.999
DON'T PUT ME
IN THE POSITION

05:36.001 --> 05:40.732
WHERE I HAVE TO AGREE
WITH KEVIN ON THIS.

05:40.734 --> 05:42.398
ON WHAT?

05:42.400 --> 05:46.931
YOUR FITNESS AS A MOTHER.

05:46.933 --> 05:48.865
I WON'T.

05:48.867 --> 05:55.665
♪♪

06:00.133 --> 06:02.598
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

06:02.600 --> 06:04.998
ME. COME IN?

06:05.000 --> 06:06.765
DON'T MIND IF I DO.

06:08.467 --> 06:10.065
GO AWAY.

06:10.067 --> 06:12.165
SO AUSTERE.

06:13.867 --> 06:15.532
LEAVE ME ALONE.

06:20.434 --> 06:22.498
I'M SORRY.

06:22.500 --> 06:24.432
CONGRATULATIONS.

06:27.334 --> 06:29.332
I SHOULDN'T HAVE
TALKED ABOUT...

06:29.334 --> 06:32.698
YOU KNOW, I -- I DIDN'T KNOW
YOU WERE REALLY SICK.

06:32.700 --> 06:35.065
WHO TOLD YOU TO COME HERE?

06:35.067 --> 06:37.431
NO ONE.
LIE.

06:37.433 --> 06:40.365
GRANDMA, BUT IT'S TRUE.

06:40.367 --> 06:42.332
I FORGIVE YOU.

06:42.334 --> 06:44.465
GO TO HELL.

06:44.467 --> 06:48.132
WOW. OKAY. WOW.

06:48.134 --> 06:49.598
SERIOUSLY?

06:49.600 --> 06:51.532
YOU'RE GOING TO ACT
LIKE I HURT YOUR FEELINGS,

06:51.534 --> 06:53.098
YOUR SENSE OF DECENCY?

06:53.100 --> 06:54.732
YOU MADE A JOKE ABOUT ME
GETTING PREGNANT

06:54.734 --> 06:58.631
RIGHT BEFORE MY OVARIES DIED,
RIGHT BEFORE I FELL OVER.

06:58.633 --> 07:01.565
I KNOW.
I'M TRYING TO APOLOGIZE.

07:01.567 --> 07:04.365
I DON'T WANT AN APOLOGY OR
ANYTHING FROM ANYBODY LIKE YOU.

07:04.367 --> 07:06.665
GET OUT.
ANYBODY LIKE ME?

07:06.667 --> 07:09.665
GET OUT!
THANKS FOR THE UPDATE!

07:18.534 --> 07:21.132
SWEETHEART?

07:21.134 --> 07:22.665
I DON'T WANT
TO TALK ABOUT IT.

07:22.667 --> 07:24.965
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

07:33.200 --> 07:35.465
[ RINGING CONTINUES ]

07:35.467 --> 07:36.932
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

07:36.934 --> 07:38.198
HEY.

07:38.200 --> 07:41.132
IS THAT LEGAL DEFENSE FUND
OF YOURS OPERATIONAL YET,

07:41.134 --> 07:43.065
LIKE, FUNDED?

07:43.067 --> 07:44.132
WHY?

07:44.134 --> 07:45.598
Woman in Collierville
just killed her husband

07:45.600 --> 07:48.131
While he was sleeping.

07:48.133 --> 07:50.398
SHE'S SAYING
IT WAS SELF-DEFENSE.

07:50.400 --> 07:54.132
♪♪

07:54.134 --> 07:56.465
[ SIGHS ]

07:56.467 --> 08:00.198
♪♪

08:00.200 --> 08:02.065
COME IN.
HMM.

08:02.067 --> 08:04.032
I'M ALLOWED
TO VISIT AGAIN, HUH?

08:04.034 --> 08:06.465
WELL,
YOU ARE HERE ON BUSINESS.

08:06.467 --> 08:10.398
HUH, BOY, GO, STAY,
BUSINESS, PLEASURE.

08:10.400 --> 08:11.665
[ CHUCKLES ]

08:11.667 --> 08:13.465
KEEPING UP WITH YOU
IS A WORKOUT.

08:13.467 --> 08:15.265
WELL, I'M GRATEFUL
FOR THE FLEXIBILITY.

08:15.267 --> 08:16.665
UH-HUH.

08:16.667 --> 08:18.998
[ CHUCKLES ]

08:19.000 --> 08:21.065
YOU SAID IN YOUR TEXT

08:21.067 --> 08:23.932
THAT YOU MIGHT BE ABLE
TO HELP WITH THE TAX BILL?

08:23.934 --> 08:26.132
YES, UH,
SO LET'S GET RIGHT TO IT.

08:26.134 --> 08:27.398
WELL, NO, I JUST MEANT THAT --
NO, NO, NO.

08:27.400 --> 08:31.198
WE'RE HERE TO TALK BUSINESS,
SO LET'S TALK.

08:31.200 --> 08:33.265
WHAT DO YOU KNOW
ABOUT CRYPTOCURRENCIES?

08:33.267 --> 08:35.465
NOTHING.
AND BLOCKCHAIN?

08:35.467 --> 08:37.798
LESS.
THAT'S WHAT I THOUGHT.

08:37.800 --> 08:40.732
JUST LIKE BACK IN ROME,
NOBODY KNEW ABOUT JESUS,

08:40.734 --> 08:43.132
AND HE WAS THERE READY
TO SAVE THEIR LIVES.

08:43.134 --> 08:45.332
HMM, YOU BETTER PREACH.

08:45.334 --> 08:47.899
NOW PEOPLE ARE
GETTING RICH QUICK.

08:54.000 --> 08:55.132
CAN WE?

08:57.567 --> 08:59.565
HAS SHE COME DOWNSTAIRS YET?

08:59.567 --> 09:00.598
MARICEL: No, ma'am, she hasn't.

09:00.600 --> 09:02.132
IS SHE STILL ON THAT SOFA?

09:02.134 --> 09:05.665
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

09:05.667 --> 09:06.732
HER CAR JUST PULLED UP.

09:06.734 --> 09:09.865
OH, I'LL BE RIGHT THERE.

09:09.867 --> 09:11.332
MARICEL, I HAVE TO GO.
LISTEN.

09:11.334 --> 09:15.065
I want you to tell Javier
to go outside to the fuse box.

09:15.067 --> 09:17.931
TURN OFF THE POWER
IN HER SUITE FOR AWHILE.

09:17.933 --> 09:21.265
DESPERATE TIMES CALL
FOR DESPERATE MEASURES.

09:21.267 --> 09:22.865
MM-HMM.

09:22.867 --> 09:24.865
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

09:27.400 --> 09:28.798
LOOK AT THIS.

09:28.800 --> 09:31.598
PEOPLE DON'T KNOW HOW TO ACT,
BUT I KIND OF GET IT.

09:31.600 --> 09:33.598
SHE IS MAXINE PATTERSON,
AFTER ALL.

09:33.600 --> 09:35.332
WELL, SHE'S JUST
A PERSON NOW.

09:35.334 --> 09:37.732
YEAH. YOU'RE RIGHT.
I KNOW, LADY MAE,

09:37.734 --> 09:39.732
BUT EVERYBODY
JUST NEEDS TO CALM DO--

09:39.734 --> 09:41.065
OH, MY GOD. THERE SHE IS.

09:41.067 --> 09:42.932
[ LAUGHS ]

09:42.934 --> 09:44.798
OH, LORD, HAVE MERCY.

09:44.800 --> 09:47.332
-GOD BLESS YOU.
-MAXINE.

09:47.334 --> 09:49.398
OH, MAE.

09:49.400 --> 09:50.932
OH, MY GOSH.

09:50.934 --> 09:54.332
EVERYONE, I WANT YOU
TO MEET MY DEAR FRIEND,

09:54.334 --> 09:56.532
PASTOR MAXINE PATTERSON.

09:56.534 --> 10:00.199
AND, MAXINE,
THIS IS CALVARY.

10:00.201 --> 10:02.465
OH.

10:02.467 --> 10:04.465
[ APPLAUSE ]

10:04.467 --> 10:06.932
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

10:06.934 --> 10:08.332
LISTEN. LISTEN.

10:08.334 --> 10:10.132
I'LL BE HERE FOR A MINUTE,

10:10.134 --> 10:12.665
BUT AS SOON AS I'M FINISHED,
WE CAN CATCH UP.

10:12.667 --> 10:16.065
I CAN SIGN AUTOGRAPHS,
TAKE PHOTOS, BUT RIGHT NOW,

10:16.067 --> 10:18.798
I NEED SOME TIME
WITH THE FIRST LADY.

10:18.800 --> 10:19.865
LET ME ON THROUGH.

10:19.867 --> 10:22.332
FOLLOW ME, PLEASE,
WOMEN OF GOD.

10:22.334 --> 10:24.732
NOW I DO KNOW
WHERE MY OFFICE IS.

10:24.734 --> 10:27.398
FOLLOW ME, SISTER WARRIORS.
COMING THROUGH.

10:27.400 --> 10:30.732
OOH, SHE IS A PIECE OF WORK,
THAT ONE.

10:30.734 --> 10:32.665
OH, SHE'S ADORABLE,

10:32.667 --> 10:34.065
AND YOU DON'T KNOW
THE HALF OF IT.

10:34.067 --> 10:36.265
I BET YOU'RE RIGHT.

10:36.267 --> 10:37.865
SO YOU'RE ON YOUR WAY
TO GRACE'S?

10:37.867 --> 10:41.532
YEAH.
GREENLEAF TO GREENLEAF.

10:41.534 --> 10:43.532
UH, YOU KNOW, ABOUT THAT
WEBSITE YOU MENTIONED...

10:43.534 --> 10:46.065
YES, COINDESK,
YOU GOT TO CHECK THAT OUT.

10:46.067 --> 10:47.132
UH...

10:47.134 --> 10:49.065
BISHOP.
MAXINE.

10:49.067 --> 10:50.398
BEEN SO LONG.

10:50.400 --> 10:52.465
WHAT A SURPRISE.

10:52.467 --> 10:54.665
MAE DIDN'T TELL YOU
I WAS STOPPING BY?

10:54.667 --> 10:57.531
YOU KNOW, AS A MATTER OF FACT,
SHE DIDN'T.

10:57.533 --> 10:58.865
MM-HMM.

10:58.867 --> 11:00.532
WE HAVE A LOT
TO CATCH UP ON.

11:00.534 --> 11:02.799
HOW LONG HAS IT BEEN,
FOREVER?

11:02.801 --> 11:04.065
AND A DAY.

11:04.067 --> 11:06.131
[ LAUGHING ]

11:06.133 --> 11:08.798
WELL, I CAN'T WAIT
TO HAVE YOU TO MYSELF,

11:08.800 --> 11:10.598
SO MUCH TO TALK
TO YOU ABOUT.

11:10.600 --> 11:13.165
-YES, FIRST LADY.
-MM-HMM.

11:14.967 --> 11:17.231
MAXINE PATTERSON, HUH?

11:17.233 --> 11:19.965
I WONDER WHAT MAE IS UP TO.

11:19.967 --> 11:21.865
THE DEVIL ONLY KNOWS.

11:24.267 --> 11:26.532
EXCUSE ME.
MM-HMM.

11:31.034 --> 11:33.098
SO SHE KILLED HIM
WITH A HAMMER,

11:33.100 --> 11:35.432
WHICH SOUNDS UNATTRACTIVE
IF YOU'RE SOMEONE WHO'S THINKING

11:35.434 --> 11:37.132
ABOUT BACKING HER,
BUT APPARENTLY,

11:37.134 --> 11:39.798
IT'S SOMETHING HE'D USED
ON HER A FEW TIMES BEFORE.

11:39.800 --> 11:40.932
HMM.
MM-HMM.

11:40.934 --> 11:42.798
IS THAT A CUSTOM SHIRT?

11:42.800 --> 11:44.398
EXCUSE ME?

11:44.400 --> 11:46.698
THE SHIRT YOU'RE WEARING, DID --
DID YOU HAVE IT MADE?

11:46.700 --> 11:48.665
NO, JUST OFF THE RACK.

11:48.667 --> 11:52.198
REALLY?
IT JUST FITS YOU SO WELL.

11:52.200 --> 11:53.665
DID YOU PICK THAT OUT?

11:53.667 --> 11:56.332
MNH-MNH.
HE DOES HIS OWN SHOPPING.

11:56.334 --> 11:57.931
IMPRESSIVE.

11:57.933 --> 11:59.732
YOU KNOW, SO MANY MEN,
WELL, MEN WITH MONEY,

11:59.734 --> 12:00.798
SOME OF MY MALE CLIENTS,

12:00.800 --> 12:04.132
I MEAN, THEY PUT
NO THOUGHT INTO CLOTHES,

12:04.134 --> 12:06.798
AND WHERE IT SHOWS
IS AROUND THE NECK

12:06.800 --> 12:09.932
RIGHT UP HERE BY THE OPENING,
AND -- AND YOURS IS --

12:09.934 --> 12:12.899
IT OPENS JUST RIGHT.
[ LAUGHS ]

12:14.867 --> 12:19.198
WELL, THANK YOU.
YEAH.

12:19.200 --> 12:21.465
YOU WANT TO HEAR ANY MORE
ABOUT THIS CASE, ROCHELLE?

12:21.467 --> 12:24.998
YOU CAN JUST TAKE A LOOK AT IT
ON YOUR OWN AND DECIDE THEN.

12:25.000 --> 12:27.332
GRACE, I TRUST YOU.

12:27.334 --> 12:29.932
LOOK, I KNOW YOU HAVE
THE GIFT OF DISCERNMENT,

12:29.934 --> 12:32.732
BUT IF YOU SAY
THAT THIS IS THE CASE,

12:32.734 --> 12:34.431
THEN THIS IS THE CASE.

12:34.433 --> 12:35.899
ALL RIGHT THEN.
THAT'S SETTLED.

12:35.901 --> 12:38.765
ALL RIGHT. NOW TELL ME
MORE ABOUT BEING A REPORTER.

12:38.767 --> 12:41.498
THAT HAS TO BE
AN EXCITING JOB.

12:41.500 --> 12:44.532
♪♪

12:44.534 --> 12:46.198
SO I COULD
COME IN THURSDAY?

12:46.200 --> 12:47.798
UH, IF YOU COULD.

12:47.800 --> 12:49.798
GLORIA,
CAN I COME ON THURSDAY?

12:49.800 --> 12:51.398
IF YOU FLY IN
THAT MORNING.

12:51.400 --> 12:54.932
NO PROBLEM.
I'M GOING AWAY SUNDAY TO CORFU.

12:54.934 --> 12:58.199
CORFU?
BEAUTIFUL PLACE.

12:58.201 --> 13:00.199
WELL, WE'LL CROSS THAT BRIDGE
WHEN WE COME TO IT,

13:00.201 --> 13:03.865
BUT RIGHT NOW, I AM SO HAPPY
TO NAIL DOWN THESE DATES.

13:05.767 --> 13:08.232
GLORIA, CAN YOU
GIVE ME A MOMENT?

13:09.000 --> 13:11.132
UH, KARAN...

13:11.134 --> 13:14.398
YES?
...WOULD YOU, PLEASE?

13:14.400 --> 13:17.198
OH, YEAH. SORRY.

13:17.200 --> 13:19.065
HOLLER IF YOU
NEED ANYTHING.

13:19.067 --> 13:21.198
YES.
I'LL BE RIGHT OUTSIDE

13:21.200 --> 13:22.898
RIGHT OVER HERE.

13:22.900 --> 13:25.665
SO WHAT IS THIS ABOUT,
CHARITY?

13:25.667 --> 13:27.165
WELL, WHAT ISN'T IT?

13:27.167 --> 13:30.498
FIRST OF ALL, SHE WAS GOING OUT
ON THIS GOSPEL TOUR,

13:30.500 --> 13:32.365
AND THEN THAT WENT UP
IN SMOKE, POOR BABY,

13:32.367 --> 13:34.632
AND THEN SHE RAN OFF
WITH A BABY,

13:34.634 --> 13:38.198
AND HER EX CALLED THE POLICE,
AND NOW SHE'S ON PILLS.

13:38.200 --> 13:40.265
WHAT KIND OF PILLS?
OH, I DON'T KNOW,

13:40.267 --> 13:43.432
SOMETHING THAT THEY GAVE HER
AFTER THE CESAREAN.

13:43.434 --> 13:45.598
SHE'S EVEN TAKING
SLEEPING PILLS.

13:45.600 --> 13:47.532
WHY IS SHE IN SUCH A STATE?

13:47.534 --> 13:49.898
THE BREAKUP, WHO KNOWS?

13:49.900 --> 13:53.565
HONESTLY,
I AM AT A LOSS.

13:53.567 --> 13:54.865
OKAY.

13:54.867 --> 13:58.599
SOMETIMES,
GOD NEEDS A LITTLE HELP.

13:58.601 --> 14:00.932
HE ORDERS ALL YOUR STEPS,

14:00.934 --> 14:03.732
AND SOMETIMES,
HE GIVES YOU A WALKER,

14:03.734 --> 14:08.165
HELP YOU PUT YOUR SHOES ON
SO THAT YOU CAN GET TO STEPPING.

14:10.800 --> 14:12.932
PASTOR, MAKE IT PLAIN.

14:12.934 --> 14:14.598
I KNOW A DOCTOR.

14:14.600 --> 14:16.398
WHAT KIND OF DOCTOR?

14:16.400 --> 14:19.532
A SOUL DOCTOR,
CERTIFIED.

14:19.534 --> 14:21.332
BUT IS THE DOCTOR
DISCREET?

14:21.334 --> 14:24.065
NO, AND THAT'S HER GIFT.

14:24.067 --> 14:27.965
LET ME -- LET ME CALL.
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

14:27.967 --> 14:29.832
ALL RIGHT, PASTOR.
YOU KEEP ME UP-TO-DATE ON THAT.

14:29.834 --> 14:30.932
YES, MA'AM, I WILL.
I'LL LET YOU KNOW

14:30.934 --> 14:32.631
AS SOON AS I TALK
TO OUR LEGAL TEAM.

14:32.633 --> 14:35.165
YOU DO THAT.
SIR. [ GIGGLES ]

14:35.167 --> 14:38.732
Y'ALL, TAKE CARE.

14:38.734 --> 14:41.598
OOH, SHE LIKES YOU.
JEALOUS?

14:41.600 --> 14:43.265
[ SCOFFS ] NO.

14:43.267 --> 14:45.865
INTERESTED, YEAH.

14:45.867 --> 14:48.998
SHE'S PLAYING ME.
SHE'S GOOD.

14:49.000 --> 14:49.865
HMM.
SEE YOU LATER.

14:49.867 --> 14:51.665
OKAY.

14:51.667 --> 15:00.665
♪♪

15:00.667 --> 15:09.332
♪♪

15:09.334 --> 15:18.865
♪♪

15:18.867 --> 15:22.998
MS. GREENLEAF,
IS THAT MY PHONE?

15:23.000 --> 15:27.365
♪♪

15:27.367 --> 15:28.732
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

15:28.734 --> 15:32.099
Mae:
CHARITY, I'M COMING IN.

15:35.734 --> 15:39.265
[ SIGHS ]

15:39.267 --> 15:42.932
I JUST PUT NATHAN DOWN, MAMA.
WE'RE FINE.

15:42.934 --> 15:45.799
BABY, I GOT YOU SOME HELP.

15:45.801 --> 15:48.065
I DON'T NEED ANY HELP.

15:48.067 --> 15:51.599
WOULD YOU PLEASE
JUST GIVE HER A CHANCE?

15:51.601 --> 15:53.732
GIVE WHO A CHANCE?

15:57.067 --> 15:59.565
HELLO, BELOVED.

15:59.567 --> 16:03.732
I'M DR. VANZANT,

16:03.734 --> 16:08.332
AND YOUR MOM SEEMS TO THINK
THAT YOU HAVE A PROBLEM.

16:08.334 --> 16:13.632
♪♪

16:16.301 --> 16:18.565
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

16:21.900 --> 16:24.798
YOU KNOW THE RULES --

16:24.800 --> 16:30.265
NO PHONES, NO COMPUTERS
AND NO CONTACTING THAT BOY,

16:30.267 --> 16:32.132
OR HAVE I NOT BEEN CLEAR?

16:32.134 --> 16:34.532
NO. NO.
YOU'VE BEEN PERFECTLY CLEAR.

16:34.534 --> 16:36.332
AND NOW YOU'RE GOING
THROUGH PEOPLE'S THINGS

16:36.334 --> 16:37.365
LIKE SOME LITTLE THIEF?

16:37.367 --> 16:38.865
DIDN'T I SAY
I WAS SORRY?

16:38.867 --> 16:41.865
WHEN YOU ARE HOME,
YOU WILL BE IN THIS ROOM,

16:41.867 --> 16:43.598
OR YOU'LL BE WITH ME.

16:43.600 --> 16:45.065
IT'S LIKE PRISON.

16:45.067 --> 16:47.332
FOR YOU AND ME BOTH.

16:47.334 --> 16:50.498
IF YOU THINK I IMAGINE
IT'S SOME KIND OF SPECIAL PRIZE

16:50.500 --> 16:51.965
TO BE SPENDING TIME
WITH SOMEBODY

16:51.967 --> 16:55.798
WHO IS SO FULL OF DISRESPECT
AND SO LACKING IN GRATITUDE

16:55.800 --> 16:59.365
FOR EVERYTHING THAT GOD HAS
GIVEN YOU, YOU THINK AGAIN!

16:59.367 --> 17:01.498
NOW YOU GOT ME WONDERING
WHAT I DID WRONG

17:01.500 --> 17:02.765
PULLING THIS KIND
OF DETAIL.

17:02.767 --> 17:04.632
I'M NOT HAVING IT.
YOU HEAR ME?

17:04.634 --> 17:06.465
YOU WILL NOT --
I HATE IT HERE.

17:06.467 --> 17:11.065
OH, WHAT YOU HATE
IS YOURSELF

17:11.067 --> 17:14.065
BECAUSE, IF YOU DIDN'T,
YOU WOULD NOT BE TRYING

17:14.067 --> 17:17.098
TO TALK TO THIS BOY
WHO HAS HURT YOU.

17:17.100 --> 17:20.265
NOW I WANT YOU
TO THINK ABOUT THAT.

17:20.267 --> 17:26.598
♪♪

17:26.600 --> 17:30.532
♪♪

17:30.534 --> 17:33.532
[ DOOR SLAMS ]

17:33.534 --> 17:36.398
[ SCREAMS ]

17:36.400 --> 17:37.565
[ BANGS ON DESK ]

17:37.567 --> 17:39.499
LOOK. I -- I'M SORRY
THAT YOU CAME

17:39.501 --> 17:42.632
ALL THIS WAY,
BUT IT'S NO USE.

17:42.634 --> 17:43.965
OKAY.

17:43.967 --> 17:45.898
I AM NOT GOING TO FIGHT YOU
FOR YOUR HEALING,

17:45.900 --> 17:47.832
BUT BEFORE I GO,
I JUST WANT YOU TO KNOW THAT,

17:47.834 --> 17:50.665
WHEN I LOOK AT YOU,

17:50.667 --> 17:55.065
I SEE SO MANY BREAKS
IN SO MANY PLACES,

17:55.067 --> 17:57.865
AND ALL I SEE IS PAIN.

17:57.867 --> 17:59.999
YEAH, WELL,
I'M NOT IN PAIN.

18:00.001 --> 18:01.598
THEN WHY TAKE PAINKILLERS?

18:01.600 --> 18:03.932
BECAUSE I HAD
ONE BAD NIGHT.

18:03.934 --> 18:05.832
AND WHAT ABOUT
THIS MORNING?

18:05.834 --> 18:09.398
I UNDERSTAND THAT YOU SLEPT
THROUGH YOUR SON CRYING.

18:09.400 --> 18:12.332
DID THAT HAPPEN?

18:12.334 --> 18:15.732
YEAH, SURE.

18:15.734 --> 18:17.799
COME ON, BELOVED. COME ON.

18:17.801 --> 18:19.332
[ SIGHS ]

18:19.334 --> 18:21.532
DON'T THINK OF IT AS HELP,

18:21.534 --> 18:24.132
JUST AN OPPORTUNITY
TO SPEAK YOUR TRUTH.

18:24.134 --> 18:28.732
TELL ME WHERE IT HURTS, AND
WHAT'S THE REAL PROBLEM HERE?

18:28.734 --> 18:30.732
NO ONE CARES ABOUT ME.

18:30.734 --> 18:32.998
REALLY?

18:33.000 --> 18:34.532
YOUR MOTHER SEEMS TO CARE.

18:34.534 --> 18:36.398
NO, SHE DOESN'T CARE.

18:36.400 --> 18:38.765
SHE DOESN'T WANT ME
TO BE AN EMBARRASSMENT.

18:38.767 --> 18:43.232
DID YOU EMBARRASS HER
BY MARRYING A MAN WHO'S GAY,

18:43.234 --> 18:47.098
OR DID YOU EMBARRASS YOURSELF
BY MARRYING A MAN

18:47.100 --> 18:49.332
WHO COULD NEVER LOVE YOU
THE WAY YOU WANT TO BE LOVED?

18:49.334 --> 18:51.965
WHO TOLD YOU ABOUT KEVIN?

18:51.967 --> 18:54.698
THERE'S ALREADY
A QUESTION ON THE FLOOR.

18:54.700 --> 18:57.965
DID YOU EMBARRASS YOURSELF?

18:57.967 --> 19:00.398
I DIDN'T KNOW.

19:00.400 --> 19:01.998
REALLY?
YES.

19:02.000 --> 19:03.531
YOU DIDN'T KNOW?
I DIDN'T KNOW.

19:03.533 --> 19:06.932
NO SIGNS, NO PROBLEMS
IN THE BEDROOM?

19:06.934 --> 19:08.532
NOTHING.
HE HID IT FROM YOU?

19:08.534 --> 19:11.998
OF COURSE!
OF COURSE HE HID IT FROM ME!

19:12.000 --> 19:14.398
I JUST FIND IT
HARD TO BELIEVE

19:14.400 --> 19:16.665
THAT SOMEBODY CAN HIDE

19:16.667 --> 19:19.932
A SECRET THAT BIG,
BUT YOU KNOW WHAT?

19:19.934 --> 19:24.399
THERE ARE SOME SECRETS THAT ARE
JUST TOO TERRIFYING TO FACE.

19:28.634 --> 19:30.598
HE MADE ME FEEL SAFE.

19:30.600 --> 19:31.932
SAFE?

19:31.934 --> 19:33.598
AND WHAT'S THE DISTINCTION

19:33.600 --> 19:38.699
THAT YOU MAKE BETWEEN BEING
UNSAFE AND BEING UNWANTED?

19:42.701 --> 19:47.632
WHEN DID YOU START FEELING OR
BELIEVING THAT YOU WEREN'T SAFE?

19:47.634 --> 19:57.132
♪♪

19:57.134 --> 19:58.732
I'VE NEVER FELT SAFE.

19:58.734 --> 20:01.132
NEVER?

20:01.134 --> 20:04.198
YOU LIVE IN THIS GREAT
BIG BEAUTIFUL HOUSE

20:04.200 --> 20:08.365
BEHIND A GATE WITH A GUARD,
AND YOU DON'T FEEL SAFE?

20:08.367 --> 20:11.299
WHY WOULDN'T YOU FEEL SAFE?

20:11.301 --> 20:13.932
♪♪

20:13.934 --> 20:16.665
MAYBE THE REAL
QUESTION IS...

20:16.667 --> 20:22.665
♪♪

20:22.667 --> 20:26.598
WHAT WOULD IT TAKE
FOR YOU TO FEEL SAFE?

20:26.600 --> 20:32.198
♪♪

20:32.200 --> 20:37.532
TO FEEL SAFE AND WANTED.

20:37.534 --> 20:43.465
YEAH, SAFE AND WANTED.

20:43.467 --> 20:45.198
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

20:45.200 --> 20:46.398
HEY.

20:46.400 --> 20:49.398
Sophia: HEY.

20:49.400 --> 20:52.598
THANKS FOR THIS.

20:52.600 --> 20:54.432
YOU'RE WELCOME.

20:56.467 --> 20:58.865
SORRY I'M SUCH A BUZZKILL.

20:58.867 --> 21:00.465
YOU DON'T NEED
TO APOLOGIZE.

21:05.001 --> 21:06.065
[ GROANS ]

21:06.067 --> 21:07.798
DOES IT STILL HURT?

21:07.800 --> 21:12.932
A LITTLE IF I SIT UP
TOO FAST.

21:15.367 --> 21:19.198
YOU WANT TO PRAY?

21:19.200 --> 21:21.132
NOT REALLY.

21:21.134 --> 21:22.932
YOU KNOW,
WHEN I BROKE MY SHOULDER,

21:22.934 --> 21:25.365
PRAYING WAS THE ONLY THING
THAT SEEMED TO HELP.

21:25.367 --> 21:27.365
YOU COULDN'T
PITCH ANYMORE.

21:27.367 --> 21:28.765
IT SUCKED.

21:28.767 --> 21:29.965
I'LL NEVER HAVE KIDS,

21:29.967 --> 21:32.632
AND I HAVE TO TAKE HORMONES
FOR THE REST OF MY LIFE.

21:32.634 --> 21:35.465
IT'S A LITTLE DIFFERENT.

21:35.467 --> 21:36.998
YOU'RE RIGHT. LOOK. I JUST MEANT
THAT I UNDERSTAND --

21:37.000 --> 21:38.699
WHAT AM I SUPPOSED
TO SAY TO GOD ANYWAYS?

21:38.701 --> 21:40.632
THANK YOU?

21:40.634 --> 21:44.398
[ SCOFFS ] HE DID THIS.

21:44.400 --> 21:46.065
NO, HE DIDN'T.

21:46.067 --> 21:47.865
THEN WHO DID?

21:47.867 --> 21:49.198
GOD IS IN CONTROL
OF EVERYTHING, ISN'T HE?

21:49.200 --> 21:50.532
AND IF, -- IF HE ISN'T,

21:50.534 --> 21:53.998
IT'S BECAUSE HE CHOOSES
NOT TO BE, RIGHT?

21:54.000 --> 21:56.565
WHO DID IT?
I DON'T KNOW.

21:56.567 --> 21:59.999
ABRAHAM'S WIFE, SAMSON'S MOTHER,
JOSEPH AND JACOB'S,

22:00.001 --> 22:01.465
THE BIBLE IS FULL OF WOMEN
WHO WERE BARREN

22:01.467 --> 22:03.465
BUT LATER HAD KIDS.

22:07.067 --> 22:08.731
BARREN?

22:08.733 --> 22:10.198
YEAH.

22:10.200 --> 22:13.332
I'M NOT BARREN.
I'M STERILE.

22:13.334 --> 22:15.532
THEY MEAN THE SAME THING.

22:15.534 --> 22:17.598
NO, THEY DON'T,

22:17.600 --> 22:19.598
AND IF YOU'D EVER LOST MORE
THAN A PITCHING ARM,

22:19.600 --> 22:22.631
YOU'D KNOW THAT,
BUT YOU DON'T.

22:22.633 --> 22:24.898
I'LL JUST COME
SEE YOU TOMORROW.

22:24.900 --> 22:33.265
♪♪

22:33.267 --> 22:38.131
♪♪

22:38.133 --> 22:41.065
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

22:41.067 --> 22:42.899
COME IN.

22:46.600 --> 22:49.598
I WANT TO CALL MY MOM.

22:49.600 --> 22:52.299
OF COURSE. BE MY GUEST.

22:54.334 --> 22:56.798
[ TELEPHONE KEYPAD BEEPING ]

22:56.800 --> 22:58.999
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

23:01.600 --> 23:02.865
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

23:02.867 --> 23:04.298
HELLO?

23:04.300 --> 23:05.832
I WANT TO COME HOME.

23:05.834 --> 23:07.465
Why? What happened?

23:07.467 --> 23:09.999
OH, YOU SAID I CAN COME HOME
IF I WANTED TO,

23:10.001 --> 23:12.098
AND I WANT TO NOW.

23:12.100 --> 23:13.398
I'll be good.
I promise.

23:13.400 --> 23:15.198
I'LL TALK TO YOUR DAD.

23:15.200 --> 23:17.432
OKAY.
I LOVE YOU, MOM. GOOD NIGHT.

23:18.934 --> 23:21.032
[ TELEPHONE BEEPS ]

23:27.734 --> 23:30.065
[ TRAIN WHISTLE BLOWS
IN DISTANCE ]

23:34.067 --> 23:36.998
[ EXHALES ]

23:37.000 --> 23:40.732
HEY, FIRST LADY.
GOT A SEC?

23:40.734 --> 23:42.665
WHAT HAPPENED?

23:42.667 --> 23:45.032
ZORA JUST ASKED
TO COME HOME.

23:45.034 --> 23:46.098
OH, NO.

23:46.100 --> 23:48.598
I TOLD HER
THAT WE WOULD DISCUSS IT.

23:48.600 --> 23:49.699
WE JUST DID.

23:49.701 --> 23:51.699
JACOB.
LOOK.

23:51.701 --> 23:55.631
WE AGREED THAT MY MOTHER TAKING
ZORA WAS BEST FOR EVERYBODY.

23:55.633 --> 23:57.431
SHE'S MISERABLE
OVER THERE.

23:57.433 --> 23:58.565
THAT MEANS IT'S WORKING.

23:58.567 --> 24:00.598
WE DIDN'T SEND HER
OVER THERE TO HAVE FUN.

24:00.600 --> 24:02.398
I KNOW BUT --
LOOK.

24:02.400 --> 24:03.732
YOU TOLD HER
WE'D DISCUSS IT.

24:03.734 --> 24:05.932
THANKS FOR GIVING ME THE VETO.
I'M USING IT.

24:05.934 --> 24:07.732
THE ANSWER IS NO.

24:10.267 --> 24:12.732
<i> AND TODAY, THE SHELBY COUNTY</i>
<i> COURTHOUSE DISTRICT ATTORNEY,</i>

24:12.734 --> 24:14.865
<i> BRENT CALUM,</i>
<i> HELD A PRESS CONFERENCE</i>

24:14.867 --> 24:16.465
<i> WITH THE FAMILY</i>
<i> OF THE DECEASED,</i>

24:16.467 --> 24:18.198
<i> VOWING TO SEEK</i>
<i> THE DEATH PENALTY</i>

24:18.200 --> 24:21.465
<i> AGAINST THE ACCUSED,</i>
<i> CORALIE HUNTER.</i>

24:21.467 --> 24:23.198
HEY, SWEETHEART.

24:23.200 --> 24:24.398
HEY.

24:24.400 --> 24:26.265
HOW'D IT GO
WITH ROBERTO?

24:26.267 --> 24:28.998
I DON'T THINK
IT'S GOING TO WORK OUT.

24:29.000 --> 24:30.732
WHY?

24:30.734 --> 24:33.465
WELL, IT'S JUST NOT
A GOOD FIT ANYMORE.

24:33.467 --> 24:34.532
SAYS WHO, HIM?

24:34.534 --> 24:36.132
ME.

24:36.134 --> 24:38.532
COME HERE, BABY.
NO.

24:38.534 --> 24:39.865
COME HERE. SIT DOWN.

24:39.867 --> 24:41.699
[ SIGHS ]

24:45.467 --> 24:47.632
WHAT'S REALLY
GOING ON, HMM?

24:50.000 --> 24:52.931
CAN YOU PLEASE DO
LITTLE SAINTS FOR ME SUNDAY?

24:52.933 --> 24:56.332
YOU'RE NOT GOING TO FEEL
WELL ENOUGH TO PREACH?

24:56.334 --> 25:01.198
HOW CAN I STAND THERE AND TELL
KIDS GOD IS GOOD WHEN HE ISN'T?

25:01.200 --> 25:04.265
OH. SOPHIA.

25:04.267 --> 25:06.732
HE'S NOT!

25:06.734 --> 25:08.598
I'M NOT GOING
TO CHURCH ANYMORE.

25:08.600 --> 25:11.598
OKAY. OKAY.

25:11.600 --> 25:13.332
YOU QUIT GOING.

25:13.334 --> 25:14.732
BUT, BABY --

25:14.734 --> 25:16.332
YOU QUIT GOING
FOR 20 YEARS.

25:16.334 --> 25:18.798
AND THAT WAS A MISTAKE,
SWEETHEART.

25:18.800 --> 25:22.032
DARIUS NEVER GOES
EXCEPT FOR WORK.

25:22.034 --> 25:25.065
IT'S ALL JUST A -- A RACKET.
THINGS JUST HAPPEN.

25:25.067 --> 25:27.432
THAT'S ALL THERE IS.
I'M NOT GOING.

25:27.434 --> 25:32.165
♪♪

25:32.167 --> 25:34.499
[ GOLF PLAYS ON TELEVISION ]

25:34.501 --> 25:38.432
♪♪

25:38.434 --> 25:40.965
[ TELEVISION SOUND SHUTS OFF ]

25:40.967 --> 25:42.665
DR. VANZANT WANTS US
TO SIT WITH HER

25:42.667 --> 25:45.431
AND CHARITY TOMORROW MORNING
BEFORE CHURCH.

25:45.433 --> 25:47.699
I SAID I'D ASK YOU,
BUT IF YOU HAVE SOMETHING --

25:47.701 --> 25:50.165
OF COURSE,
WHATEVER WE CAN DO

25:50.167 --> 25:53.665
TO GET THAT GIRL
BACK ON HER FEET, I'M FOR.

25:53.667 --> 25:56.998
GOOD. I SAID 7 A.M.

25:57.000 --> 26:00.665
IS CHARITY
WHY MAXINE CAME?

26:00.667 --> 26:02.899
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

26:02.901 --> 26:05.299
IS THAT WHY MAXINE PATTERSON
DESCENDED FROM HEAVEN

26:05.301 --> 26:09.432
WITH HER RETINUE,
TO HELP CHARITY?

26:09.434 --> 26:11.098
I'LL SEE YOU
IN THE MORNING, JAMES.

26:11.100 --> 26:12.099
MAE?

26:12.101 --> 26:13.965
I SAID, "I'LL SEE YOU
IN THE MORNING."

26:13.967 --> 26:16.432
I HEARD WHAT YOU SAID.

26:16.434 --> 26:20.465
I ALSO HEARD
WHAT YOU DIDN'T SAY,

26:20.467 --> 26:24.065
AND I BELIEVE I KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE THINKING, TOO.

26:24.067 --> 26:25.198
YOU DON'T.

26:25.200 --> 26:27.065
WELL, EITHER WAY,

26:27.067 --> 26:30.665
TAKE A LOOK AT THAT STATEMENT
YOU WROTE FOR CHURCH TOMORROW

26:30.667 --> 26:34.732
AND ADD A FAREWELL

26:34.734 --> 26:38.532
BECAUSE THERE WON'T BE
ANOTHER CHANCE TO SAY IT.

26:38.534 --> 26:42.999
♪♪

26:46.434 --> 26:48.032
Dr. Vanzant: I WANT YOU TO SHARE
WITH YOUR PARENTS.

26:48.034 --> 26:52.798
SHARE YOUR TRUTH WITH THEM.
DON'T BE AFRAID.

26:52.800 --> 26:58.432
UM, SO WHEN I WAS GROWING UP,
I -- I FELT SCARED.

26:58.434 --> 27:00.898
WHAT DID YOU HAVE
TO BE SCARED OF?

27:00.900 --> 27:03.165
NOW SHE'S NOT ACCUSING
YOU OF ANYTHING.

27:03.167 --> 27:06.065
SHE'S SHARING WITH YOU
WHAT SHE FELT, HOW SHE FEELS,

27:06.067 --> 27:10.732
SO I'M GOING TO ASK YOU BOTH
TO JUST LET HER DO THAT.

27:10.734 --> 27:16.332
AND I FELT LIKE FAITH
AND GRACE WERE SCARED.

27:16.334 --> 27:20.998
I NEVER KNEW WHAT OF, BUT THAT
MADE ME FEEL SCARED, TOO.

27:21.000 --> 27:22.732
BUT YOU NEVER TOLD ME THAT.

27:22.734 --> 27:27.931
I ASSURE YOU, DR. VANZANT,
I NEVER KNEW ABOUT THIS.

27:27.933 --> 27:29.499
WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL US?

27:29.501 --> 27:32.432
I KNEW YOU DIDN'T
WANT TO HEAR IT.

27:32.434 --> 27:35.698
AND THAT,
THAT SCARED ME EVEN MORE.

27:35.700 --> 27:37.398
GOD, BUT, YOU KNOW,

27:37.400 --> 27:39.532
I DON'T EVEN KNOW WHAT
I'M SUPPOSED TO SAY TO THAT.

27:39.534 --> 27:42.665
I MEAN,
I JUST CANNOT APOLOGIZE

27:42.667 --> 27:44.532
FOR THE REST OF MY LIFE
TO EVERYONE.

27:44.534 --> 27:47.332
SHE'S NOT ASKING YOU
FOR AN APOLOGY.

27:47.334 --> 27:50.665
SHE'S TRYING TO EXPLAIN TO YOU
WHAT SHE'S BEEN FEELING

27:50.667 --> 27:52.998
AND WHY SHE'S BEEN
BEHAVING SO ERRATICALLY.

27:53.000 --> 27:54.465
WELL, LISTEN.
I KNOW THAT EVERYTHING

27:54.467 --> 27:56.598
WASN'T PERFECT AROUND HERE.

27:56.600 --> 28:00.131
YOU'VE TOLD HER ALL ABOUT
YOUR UNCLE, I SUPPOSE?

28:00.133 --> 28:01.798
WOULD YOU RATHER
SHE HADN'T?

28:01.800 --> 28:03.698
NO, DOCTOR.

28:03.700 --> 28:07.198
WHAT I WOULD RATHER
IS THAT PEOPLE IN THIS FAMILY

28:07.200 --> 28:11.265
JUST FOR ONCE DEMONSTRATED
SOME KIND OF BACKBONE.

28:11.267 --> 28:14.398
I MEAN, YOU WERE SCARED,

28:14.400 --> 28:16.832
BUT I CAN ASSURE YOU THAT,

28:16.834 --> 28:21.132
THAT WAS MINUSCULE COMPARED
TO WHAT LITTLE FAITH FELT

28:21.134 --> 28:23.598
OR EVEN WHAT I FELT
WHEN I WAS A LITTLE GIRL,

28:23.600 --> 28:28.598
BUT, DR. VANZANT, I NEVER, EVER
BLAMED MY MOTHER FOR ANY OF IT.

28:28.600 --> 28:31.998
I'M NOT BLAMING YOU!

28:32.000 --> 28:34.932
I'M DOING
WHAT YOU WANT ME TO DO!

28:34.934 --> 28:38.398
I'M TRYING TO GET BETTER!
MAMA, WOULD YOU JUST LISTEN?

28:38.400 --> 28:42.099
NO, NOT RIGHT NOW.

28:44.467 --> 28:47.065
IN LESS THAN AN HOUR,
I HAVE TO GO TO CHURCH

28:47.067 --> 28:50.398
AND TELL THE WHOLE WORLD
THAT I FAILED AT THE ONE THING

28:50.400 --> 28:51.998
THAT I NEVER MEANT
TO FAIL AT,

28:52.000 --> 28:55.198
SO I DON'T NEED
ANOTHER PERSON COMING AT ME

28:55.200 --> 28:57.198
AND CALLING ME OUT
RIGHT NOW.

28:57.200 --> 29:00.065
MAE, SHE DOESN'T MEAN
YOU ANY HARM.

29:00.067 --> 29:01.932
WHAT DO YOU KNOW
ABOUT HARM, JAMES?

29:01.934 --> 29:03.865
YOU ARE CRASHING
THROUGH OUR FAMILY

29:03.867 --> 29:06.132
LIKE AN OLD BULL
IN A CHINA SHOP.

29:08.567 --> 29:11.198
I AM SORRY
THAT YOU WERE SCARED.

29:11.200 --> 29:12.665
WE ARE ALL SCARED.

29:12.667 --> 29:15.598
THE WORLD IS SCARY,
BUT YOU KNOW WHAT?

29:15.600 --> 29:17.065
IF YOU DON'T HAVE FAITH
TO GO THROUGH IT,

29:17.067 --> 29:18.732
THEN PRAY FOR FAITH,

29:18.734 --> 29:20.665
AND IF YOU DON'T HAVE
THE FAITH TO PRAY,

29:20.667 --> 29:23.665
THEN PRAY FOR THAT,
BUT DON'T LOOK AT ME.

29:23.667 --> 29:27.532
DON'T BEAT ME UP.
IT WON'T FIX IT.

29:27.534 --> 29:29.531
FIX YOU.

29:29.533 --> 29:32.431
THAT'S HOW JESUS WORKS,
NOT ME.

29:32.433 --> 29:35.965
♪♪

29:35.967 --> 29:38.032
THANK YOU, DR. VANZANT.

29:38.034 --> 29:46.432
♪♪

29:46.434 --> 29:50.065
♪♪

29:50.067 --> 29:52.865
WE'RE HERE FOR YOU NOW,
SWEETHEART.

29:52.867 --> 29:55.265
NO, YOU'RE NOT,

29:55.267 --> 29:59.365
AND AFTER THIS MORNING,
I DOUBT YOU'LL EVER BE AGAIN.

29:59.367 --> 30:07.132
♪♪

30:10.000 --> 30:12.598
YOU DON'T KNOCK ANYMORE?

30:12.600 --> 30:14.199
MAE.

30:17.633 --> 30:19.032
THIS IS WHAT
I HAVE TO GIVE.

30:21.634 --> 30:24.798
YOU CAN HAVE THE HOUSE.

30:24.800 --> 30:26.765
I'LL TAKE CARE
OF THE IRS BILL.

30:28.600 --> 30:32.532
HOW?

30:32.534 --> 30:35.465
THAT'S NONE
OF YOUR CONCERN.

30:35.467 --> 30:39.565
LET IT BE, UM,
MY ADDITIONAL GIFT TO YOU,

30:39.567 --> 30:41.632
BUT YOU HAVE
TO LEAVE THE CHURCH.

30:44.400 --> 30:47.732
LET ME HAVE
"DAY WITH LADY MAE."

30:47.734 --> 30:51.665
♪♪

30:51.667 --> 30:54.665
ALL RIGHT.

30:54.667 --> 30:58.398
"DAY WITH LADY MAE,"
BUT YOU HAVE TO MOVE ON.

30:58.400 --> 31:05.732
♪♪

31:05.734 --> 31:08.499
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

31:20.467 --> 31:24.932
