32:06.334 --> 32:08.198
♪ THERE IS A LOVE AND GIVING ♪

32:08.200 --> 32:11.431
♪ THERE IS A -- THERE IS A ♪

32:11.433 --> 32:15.365
♪ THERE IS A SALVATION ♪

32:15.367 --> 32:17.098
♪ RESTORATION ♪

32:17.100 --> 32:18.832
♪ THERE'S A BOOK ♪

32:18.834 --> 32:20.632
♪ THERE IS ♪

32:20.634 --> 32:22.498
♪ YEAH ♪

32:22.500 --> 32:26.198
♪ LOVE AND GIVING ♪

32:26.200 --> 32:28.299
♪♪

32:28.301 --> 32:31.432
[ APPLAUSE ]

32:35.400 --> 32:44.732
YEAH.

32:44.734 --> 32:47.398
[ APPLAUSE CONTINUES ]

32:47.400 --> 32:50.598
♪♪

32:50.600 --> 32:52.732
AMEN.
AMEN.

32:52.734 --> 32:54.932
PLEASE BE SEATED.

32:57.734 --> 32:59.932
THE FIRST LADY
IS JOINING ME UP HERE TODAY

32:59.934 --> 33:02.265
BECAUSE WE HAVE
SOME NEWS TO SHARE.

33:02.267 --> 33:05.132
THIS NEWS IS GOING TO BE,
FOR SOME, HARD TO HEAR,

33:05.134 --> 33:07.299
AND FOR THAT
WE APOLOGIZE.

33:09.400 --> 33:13.132
BUT WE'RE ONLY HUMAN AND NEVER
CLAIMED TO BE ANYTHING BUT.

33:13.134 --> 33:14.999
ISN'T THAT RIGHT, MAE?

33:17.000 --> 33:18.232
THAT'S RIGHT.

33:21.267 --> 33:23.998
NOW THIS IS NEWS
THAT WE HAVE SHARED

33:24.000 --> 33:27.298
WITH OUR FAMILY AND FRIENDS
OVER THE PAST FEW DAYS.

33:27.300 --> 33:30.665
[ CONGREGATION MURMURING ]

33:30.667 --> 33:32.398
Way to go.

33:32.400 --> 33:33.865
WE'RE DIVORCING.

33:33.867 --> 33:37.665
[ CONGREGATION GASPS,
INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

33:37.667 --> 33:39.931
I KNOW SOME OF YOU
ARE THINKING,

33:39.933 --> 33:42.398
"WELL, HAVE THEY PRAYED
ABOUT IT?"

33:42.400 --> 33:44.598
WE HAVE.
WE HAVE.

33:44.600 --> 33:47.465
"HAVE THEY --
HAVE THEY TRIED TO WORK IT OUT?"

33:47.467 --> 33:48.865
AND WE HAVE.

33:48.867 --> 33:51.532
WE HAVE.

33:51.534 --> 33:53.665
WE WILL ALWAYS BE FAMILY.

33:53.667 --> 33:57.065
MM-HMM.

33:57.067 --> 34:02.065
AND I'M STILL YOUR BISHOP.

34:02.067 --> 34:04.165
AND I --

34:04.167 --> 34:06.999
I AM NOT
GOING AWAY JUST YET.

34:09.234 --> 34:12.065
I WILL CONTINUE ON
AS YOUR FIRST LADY

34:12.067 --> 34:16.365
UP THROUGH
"A DAY WITH LADY MAE."

34:16.367 --> 34:18.165
AND WHAT A DAY
IT WILL BE.

34:18.167 --> 34:24.598
YES, WHERE WE WILL HAVE A VERY,
VERY SPECIAL GUEST,

34:24.600 --> 34:29.598
MY DEAR, DEAR FRIEND,
MAXINE PATTERSON...

34:29.600 --> 34:32.332
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

34:32.334 --> 34:37.665
♪♪

34:37.667 --> 34:39.865
...A TRUE WOMAN OF GOD.

34:39.867 --> 34:42.398
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE CONTINUE ]

34:42.400 --> 34:45.798
♪♪

34:45.800 --> 34:48.698
AMEN. AMEN.

34:48.700 --> 34:55.732
IT WILL BE A DAY-LONG SEMINAR
ON THE HISTORIC,

34:55.734 --> 35:01.731
INDISPENSABLE POWER OF WOMEN
IN THE CHURCH.

35:01.733 --> 35:03.599
THAT'S RIGHT.

35:03.601 --> 35:04.865
HALLELUJAH.

35:04.867 --> 35:07.132
Congregation: HALLELUJAH.

35:07.134 --> 35:12.865
AND IT IS ENTITLED
"SHE CHANGES EVERYTHING."

35:12.867 --> 35:15.932
[ APPLAUSE ]

35:15.934 --> 35:22.265
SO I WANT YOU TO TELL
ALL YOUR FRIENDS FROM CALVARY

35:22.267 --> 35:25.532
TO TRIUMPH AND BEYOND,

35:25.534 --> 35:28.932
CHURCHED AND UNCHURCHED.

35:28.934 --> 35:36.465
TELL THEM,
"SHE CHANGES...

35:36.467 --> 35:37.699
EVERYTHING."

35:37.701 --> 35:40.231
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

35:40.233 --> 35:49.332
♪♪

35:49.334 --> 35:56.165
♪♪

35:56.167 --> 35:58.932
♪♪

36:02.601 --> 36:03.599
Thomas: DIDN'T THEY JUST DO
THEIR VOW CLASS

36:03.601 --> 36:04.665
FOR ALL THOSE
ENGAGED COUPLES.

36:04.667 --> 36:06.598
WELL, YOU KNOW
WHAT THEY SAY, THOMAS.

36:06.600 --> 36:09.931
THOSE WHO
CAN'T DO TEACH.

36:09.933 --> 36:12.932
Woman: THESE DIVORCES
START OUT BEING AMICABLE,

36:12.934 --> 36:16.432
BUT IT DOESN'T LAST.
IT'S THE HONEYMOON PERIOD.

36:16.434 --> 36:18.131
DID THEY TELL YOU
THIS WAS COMING?

36:18.133 --> 36:19.932
NO, NOT FOR YEARS.

36:19.934 --> 36:22.398
WHEN HAVE THEY EVER
SHARED ANYTHING IMPORTANT?

36:22.400 --> 36:24.932
I THINK IT'S TIME
FOR A CHANGE.

36:24.934 --> 36:26.598
WELL, I'LL STAY
TO SEE MAXINE,

36:26.600 --> 36:28.932
BUT AFTER THAT,
IT'S TIME TO GO.

36:28.934 --> 36:31.332
I CAN'T HAVE A PASTOR
WHO IS DIVORCED.

36:31.334 --> 36:32.665
I FEEL YOU ON THAT.

36:32.667 --> 36:34.665
WE NEED SOMEBODY
UP THERE WHO'S SOLID.

36:34.667 --> 36:37.398
YEAH.
OH, HI, PASTOR GREENLEAF.

36:37.400 --> 36:39.798
I'M SO SORRY TO HEAR
ABOUT YOUR PARENTS.

36:39.800 --> 36:41.465
YEAH, WE ALL ARE.

36:41.467 --> 36:43.198
THANK YOU.

36:43.200 --> 36:45.665
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

36:45.667 --> 36:53.332
♪♪

36:53.334 --> 36:56.398
THANK YOU SO MUCH
FOR DOING IT.

36:56.400 --> 36:59.932
OH, MAE, WHAT WE'RE
GOING THROUGH HERE NOW

36:59.934 --> 37:02.531
IS SANKOFA --
REACHING BACK,

37:02.533 --> 37:04.665
PICKING UP
WHAT YOU DROPPED.

37:04.667 --> 37:08.832
THAT'S LIFE, GIRL, AND IF
THIS DON'T GET YOU CALVARY

37:08.834 --> 37:11.765
OR THAT MAN
ON THE BRICKS,

37:11.767 --> 37:16.132
WE GOING TO MARCH UP THE ROAD
AND PLANT YOU A BRAND-NEW ONE.

37:16.134 --> 37:17.598
AMEN?
AMEN.

37:17.600 --> 37:20.465
ALL RIGHT.

37:20.467 --> 37:21.998
THANK YOU AGAIN, MAXINE.

37:22.000 --> 37:23.432
OH, YOU'RE WELCOME, BABY.

37:26.267 --> 37:31.631
DR. VANZANT, I APPRECIATE HOW
YOU CAME ON SUCH SHORT NOTICE,

37:31.633 --> 37:34.765
BUT I'LL HAVE YOU KNOW
THAT I DON'T APPRECIATE

37:34.767 --> 37:38.098
BEING BUSHWHACKED
LIKE THAT

37:38.100 --> 37:41.031
AND CERTAINLY NOT
IN MY OWN HOME.

37:41.033 --> 37:43.698
I AM SORRY
YOU FELT BUSHWHACKED.

37:43.700 --> 37:47.165
I DIDN'T FEEL BUSHWHACKED.
I WAS.

37:47.167 --> 37:50.798
BY YOUR DAUGHTER'S TRUTH,
NOT BY ME.

37:50.800 --> 37:52.299
I DIDN'T ASK YOU
TO COME HERE

37:52.301 --> 37:57.632
AND TELL MY DAUGHTER THAT
HER PROBLEMS WERE ALL MY FAULT.

37:57.634 --> 37:58.698
NO.

37:58.700 --> 38:00.465
I GET ENOUGH OF THAT
FROM MY OLDEST.

38:00.467 --> 38:03.665
I DON'T NEED IT COMING
FROM MY BABY, TOO.

38:03.667 --> 38:07.065
<i> YOU</i> DIDN'T ASK ME
TO COME,

38:07.067 --> 38:10.198
BUT WHEN YOU'RE READY
TO DEAL WITH<i> YOUR</i> PAIN,

38:10.200 --> 38:12.465
I MAKE THIS VOW.

38:12.467 --> 38:15.799
CALL ME,
AND I'LL BE THERE.

38:24.400 --> 38:28.032
YOUR FATHER AND I SPOKE,
AND WE BOTH FEEL IT'S BEST

38:28.034 --> 38:32.732
IF WE JUST STAY
THE COURSE FOR NOW.

38:32.734 --> 38:34.498
I'M SORRY.
IT'S FINE.

38:34.500 --> 38:37.465
I'LL JUST STAY AWHILE.

38:37.467 --> 38:41.865
IT'S NOT GOING TO BE EASY,
BUT I THINK IT'S WHAT I NEED.

38:45.667 --> 38:46.932
OKAY.

38:46.934 --> 38:49.532
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

38:49.534 --> 38:52.665
WELL, I GUESS I'LL GO.

38:52.667 --> 38:55.798
KISS WINKIE
AND DAD FOR ME?

38:55.800 --> 38:57.565
I WILL.

38:59.800 --> 39:02.865
[ CHUCKLES ]

39:02.867 --> 39:05.398
LISTEN. IF YOU'RE MAKING
THIS NICE AS A FAVOR TO ME,

39:05.400 --> 39:06.632
YOU DON'T HAVE TO.

39:06.634 --> 39:09.065
NO. NO. I'M NOT.

39:11.634 --> 39:14.531
I KNOW
IT'LL BE OVER SOON.

39:14.533 --> 39:17.065
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

39:17.067 --> 39:18.398
HEY. GOT A MINUTE?

39:18.400 --> 39:21.598
YEAH, A MINUTE.
I'M GOING FOR A WALK.

39:21.600 --> 39:24.398
WELL, DON'T GO TOO FAR,
SWEETHEART.

39:24.400 --> 39:25.899
WHY NOT?

39:25.901 --> 39:28.132
YOU'RE STILL WEAK.

39:28.134 --> 39:31.065
WHAT DO YOU
WANT TO TELL ME?

39:31.067 --> 39:34.532
OOH, SO A LOT HAPPENED
TODAY AT CHURCH.

39:34.534 --> 39:37.698
HMM, I KNOW.

39:37.700 --> 39:40.032
MY PHONE HAS BEEN
BLOWING UP ALL DAY,

39:40.034 --> 39:42.131
AND PASTOR MOORE WANTS TO KNOW
WHEN I'M COMING BACK

39:42.133 --> 39:43.598
TO DO THE LITTLE SAINTS
AGAIN.

39:43.600 --> 39:47.432
MM-HMM.
AND WHAT'D YOU TELL HER?

39:47.434 --> 39:49.299
I HAVEN'T TOLD HER
ANYTHING YET.

39:52.400 --> 39:55.132
WHAT DO YOU WANT ME
TO SAY, COOL?

39:55.134 --> 40:00.465
NO. UH,
I JUST WANT YOU TO KNOW,

40:00.467 --> 40:02.532
I KNOW YOU
DIDN'T GO TODAY,

40:02.534 --> 40:05.099
BUT, SWEETHEART,
YOU'RE GOING TO HAVE TO.

40:08.467 --> 40:11.532
NO. I'M NOT.

40:14.167 --> 40:16.099
I'M NOT GOING TO CHURCH
EVER AGAIN.

